OL,3,COfcom to stop issuing phone numbers if
OL,4,Cisland law not updated, warns minister
OL,6,FJersey's Minister for Sustainable
OL,7,FEconomic Development, Deputy Kirsten
OL,8,FMorel, said they were told that "there
OL,9,Fwas no legislative basis for any of
OL,10,Fthe crown dependencies to be provided
OL,11,Fwith +44 numbers".
OL,13,FHe has now told ITV News that it is
OL,14,F"absolutely critical" that the draft
OL,15,Flaw is approved.
OL,17,FGuernsey's Policy and Resources
OL,18,FCommittee has since closed the
OL,19,Floophole, passing the updated
OL,20,Flegislation by the States in March.
