OL,3,COfcom to stop issuing phone numbers if
OL,4,Cisland law not updated, warns minister
OL,6,FNow Deputy Morel says it is Jersey's
OL,7,Fturn to change the law, explaining:
OL,8,F"It is one of those strange things
OL,9,Fthat is absolutely critical.
OL,11,F"While Ofcom weren't going to take
OL,12,Faway numbers that were already
OL,13,Fallocated to the island, Jersey would,
OL,14,Fat some point, have run out of
OL,15,Ftelephone numbers.
OL,17,F"This is one of those informal
OL,18,Fsituations that now needs to be
OL,19,Fformalised."
